---
export const prerender = false;
---
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>섹션 분리 테스트 - B+C 조합</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f5f5f0; }

    .test-label {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 50;
      background: #333;
      color: #D4AA45;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 48px 24px;
    }
    .section-light { background: #fff; }
    .section-muted { background: #f5f5f0; }

    .section-sub {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.5em;
      color: #9B8A5C;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .section-title {
      margin-top: 16px;
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .section-desc {
      margin-top: 16px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* 번호 배지 */
    .section-number {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1.5px solid #D4AA45;
      color: #D4AA45;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    /* 골드 구분선 */
    .divider-line {
      border: none;
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #d4aa4580, transparent);
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* 더미 콘텐츠 */
    .dummy-content {
      margin-top: 24px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .dummy-card {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 100px;
      height: 80px;
      background: #f0efe8;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e5e0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="test-label">B + C 조합: 번호 배지 + 골드 구분선</div>

  <!-- 섹션 1 -->
  <div class="section section-light">
    <div class="section-number">01</div>
    <span class="section-sub">WHY SIMPLE CUBE</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">특별함이 필요한<br/>모든 순간을 위해</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">심플큐브는 단순한 포토부스 대여를 넘어,<br/>브랜드와 순간을 잇는 특별한 경험을 만들어 드립니다.</p>
    <div class="dummy-content">
      <div class="dummy-card"></div>
      <div class="dummy-card"></div>
      <div class="dummy-card"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="divider-line" />

  <!-- 섹션 2 -->
  <div class="section section-light">
    <div class="section-number">02</div>
    <span class="section-sub">CLIENTS</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">고객사</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">다양한 브랜드와 함께했습니다.</p>
    <div class="dummy-content">
      <div class="dummy-card"></div>
      <div class="dummy-card"></div>
      <div class="dummy-card"></div>
      <div class="dummy-card"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="divider-line" />

  <!-- 섹션 3 -->
  <div class="section section-light">
    <div class="section-number">03</div>
    <span class="section-sub">OUR STORY</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">심플큐브의 이야기</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">2019년부터 지금까지, 특별한 순간을 기록합니다.</p>
    <div class="dummy-content">
      <div class="dummy-card"></div>
      <div class="dummy-card"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
